## Create Account [/api/v2/auth/register]

### Create a New Account [POST]
You may create your own account using this action.
This action takes a JSON payload as part of the request.
Response then return specific header and body.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username": "timmutai",
            "email": "timmutai@email.com",
            "password": "12345.H",
            "confirm_password": "12345.H"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "msg": "User created successfully.",
                "user_data": {
                "email": "timmutai@email.com",
                "password": "12345.H",
                "user_id": 1,
                "username": "timmutai"
            }

